    "However, follow-up manipulations of the belief likelihood revealed that the superiority of LLaMA2 was illusory, possibly reflecting a bias towards attributing ignorance [38].Yet another of the main limitations of LLMs up until now seems to be on mathematical calculations.",
    "This is due to the modus operandi of these models, which in essence is \"predict the next word with the highest accuracy\".",
    "Humans may be impressed by the storytelling abilities of these models, but what happens when you ask them a mathematical question?",
    "LLMs perform poorly at mathematics because they don't understand the underlying mathematical rules.",
    "While they can write code to solve a mathematical problem, without the produced code they can only estimate the probability of a set of numbers to be seen together as a sequence (ie: 3 + 3 = 6)."
  ],
